请选择 Shadowsocks 加密协议 [1-7]

 1. aes-128-cfb

 2. aes-256-cfb

 3. chacha20

 4. chacha20-ietf

 5. aes-128-gcm

 6. aes-256-gcm

 7. chacha20-ietf-poly1305

(默认加密协议: chacha20-ietf-poly1305)

